WEBVTT

00:00:42.719 --> 00:00:43.560
Zhao Fengsheng

00:00:47.520 --> 00:00:49.000
We meet again.

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:50.000
Tang Hongtu

00:00:52.960 --> 00:00:54.159
Lure the tiger away from the mountain.

00:00:54.679 --> 00:00:55.520
Zhao Fengsheng

00:00:55.960 --> 00:00:57.679
You really think our Tang family

00:00:58.240 --> 00:00:59.920
is so easy for you to control?

00:01:09.239 --> 00:01:11.159
Zhao Fengsheng, oh Zhao Fengsheng.

00:01:12.760 --> 00:01:14.159
Ghost Face Hall members, listen up!

00:01:14.519 --> 00:01:15.319
Yes!

00:01:15.879 --> 00:01:17.400
Whoever finds the mine entrance

00:01:17.799 --> 00:01:18.959
will be promoted directly to Hall Master.

00:01:19.439 --> 00:01:20.760
Anyone who dares to resist,

00:01:21.519 --> 00:01:22.599
kill them on the spot.

00:01:22.680 --> 00:01:23.480
Yes, sir!

00:01:24.040 --> 00:01:26.599
Mu Jinfu assassinated Uncle Gui Lang.

00:01:26.959 --> 00:01:27.799
You people of Ghost Face Hall,

00:01:27.799 --> 00:01:29.200
want to follow such a scoundrel?

00:01:30.040 --> 00:01:31.959
Following Mr. Mu and Second Master Tang,

00:01:31.959 --> 00:01:33.920
we get to live the good life.

00:01:33.920 --> 00:01:34.879
An old man like Uncle Gui Lang,

00:01:34.879 --> 00:01:36.200
who only knows how to talk about rules,

00:01:36.239 --> 00:01:37.359
should've died long ago.

00:01:37.400 --> 00:01:38.560
Enough talk!

00:01:38.599 --> 00:01:39.400
Do it!

00:01:42.040 --> 00:01:43.000
Money, money!

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:43.400
Protect the young lady!

00:01:43.400 --> 00:01:43.920
Forget about the money!

00:01:43.920 --> 00:01:44.640
Get out of here first!

00:01:49.519 --> 00:01:51.000
Take Miss Qian and the others away first!

00:01:51.319 --> 00:01:52.120
Go!

00:01:57.040 --> 00:01:57.760
Darn it!

00:01:58.159 --> 00:01:58.879
Come on!

00:01:58.879 --> 00:02:00.400
Trying to keep the Four Pests of the Old Street here?

00:02:00.519 --> 00:02:01.480
It's not that easy!

00:02:06.799 --> 00:02:07.400
Let's go!

00:02:18.840 --> 00:02:19.840
Look at those moves.

00:02:19.879 --> 00:02:22.280
Zhao Fengsheng must be an important figure in Cloud Thunder.

00:02:22.520 --> 00:02:23.919
If we let him escape,

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:26.080
no one can withstand Cloud Thunder's retaliation.

00:02:26.800 --> 00:02:27.639
Zhao Fengsheng!

00:02:28.159 --> 00:02:30.280
You're as troublesome as your father.

00:02:30.280 --> 00:02:31.520
So you did know my father.

00:02:31.759 --> 00:02:33.240
Did you kill him?

00:02:33.759 --> 00:02:34.960
Go down and keep him company.

00:02:49.520 --> 00:02:50.319
Brother!

00:02:54.560 --> 00:02:55.360
Shengzi!

00:02:55.520 --> 00:02:56.800
Shengzi!

00:02:57.719 --> 00:02:58.639
Shengzi!

00:03:07.240 --> 00:03:08.039
Shengzi!

00:03:10.280 --> 00:03:11.479
Get to the hospital, quick!

00:03:25.039 --> 00:03:25.840
After them!

00:03:26.360 --> 00:03:27.199
Forget about chasing them!

00:03:28.159 --> 00:03:29.400
Finding the gold mine is what matters.

00:03:30.080 --> 00:03:30.879
Old Mu!

00:03:31.159 --> 00:03:33.080
Go and capture all the Qian family members for me.

00:03:33.919 --> 00:03:36.360
Take the rest and hurry to find the mine.

00:03:36.520 --> 00:03:37.360
You must be quick.

00:03:37.560 --> 00:03:38.599
You few, come with me.

00:03:38.599 --> 00:03:39.280
Follow me.

00:03:39.599 --> 00:03:41.319
You two, take the case.

00:04:01.520 --> 00:04:02.319
Miss Cui.

00:04:02.319 --> 00:04:03.479
Let me stop your bleeding first.

00:04:06.840 --> 00:04:07.639
Nurse!

00:04:08.159 --> 00:04:09.319
Can you tell me

00:04:09.599 --> 00:04:11.400
when Shengzi will wake up?

00:04:11.479 --> 00:04:12.319
I don't know.

00:04:12.360 --> 00:04:13.639
They're still operating inside.

00:04:13.919 --> 00:04:14.719
Erni.

00:04:15.159 --> 00:04:16.199
Shengzi is blessed and lucky.

00:04:16.199 --> 00:04:17.160
Stop your bleeding first.

00:04:18.439 --> 00:04:19.279
It's okay.

00:04:23.000 --> 00:04:24.120
Shengzi's life is so tough.

00:04:24.199 --> 00:04:26.160
He's made it through so many close calls.

00:04:26.439 --> 00:04:27.959
Even the Ox-Head and Horse-Face can't keep him.

00:04:29.240 --> 00:04:30.160
Right, Hualian?

00:04:30.680 --> 00:04:31.600
Brother will be fine.

00:04:32.240 --> 00:04:33.000
He's fine.

00:04:37.600 --> 00:04:38.399
Erni.

00:04:39.120 --> 00:04:40.759
I haven't had your wedding wine yet.

00:04:41.319 --> 00:04:42.519
Shengzi will definitely be okay.

00:05:00.199 --> 00:05:01.120
I need a few more people!

00:05:01.120 --> 00:05:02.480
Patient in OR three is hemorrhaging badly.

00:05:02.480 --> 00:05:03.439
He's not going to make it.

00:05:04.759 --> 00:05:05.560
Nurse!

00:05:05.800 --> 00:05:06.680
What did you say?

00:05:07.040 --> 00:05:08.240
I said he's hemorrhaging badly!

00:05:09.160 --> 00:05:10.399
Then what can I do?

00:05:10.399 --> 00:05:11.120
Draw blood.

00:05:11.279 --> 00:05:12.160
Take my blood.

00:05:12.279 --> 00:05:13.680
I'm universal type O.

00:05:14.000 --> 00:05:14.759
Take mine.

00:05:14.759 --> 00:05:15.399
I'm the same as my brother.

00:05:15.399 --> 00:05:15.879
Nurse! Nurse!

00:05:15.879 --> 00:05:16.519
Take mine.

00:05:16.519 --> 00:05:17.399
I have plenty of blood.

00:05:17.600 --> 00:05:18.519
Calm down, all of you.

00:05:18.519 --> 00:05:19.319
The patient is in critical condition.

00:05:19.319 --> 00:05:20.399
Don't delay us from saving him.

00:05:24.040 --> 00:05:25.079
Zhao Fengsheng!

00:05:25.720 --> 00:05:27.279
You jerk!

00:05:28.920 --> 00:05:29.680
I'm telling you,

00:05:29.680 --> 00:05:30.920
you better not die in there.

00:05:30.920 --> 00:05:32.120
If you dare die in there,

00:05:32.120 --> 00:05:33.439
I'll burn all your dirty magazines

00:05:33.439 --> 00:05:34.720
at your house.

00:05:57.240 --> 00:05:57.879
Doctor!

00:05:57.959 --> 00:05:58.759
How is he?

00:05:59.279 --> 00:06:00.160
I'm very sorry.

00:06:00.240 --> 00:06:01.519
We did everything we could.

00:06:02.839 --> 00:06:03.639
Doctor...

00:06:27.319 --> 00:06:28.800
Zhao Fengsheng!

00:06:30.920 --> 00:06:33.439
Don't think you can leave me behind!

00:06:34.319 --> 00:06:35.519
I'm telling you,

00:06:36.519 --> 00:06:39.079
even as a ghost I'll haunt you!

00:06:39.360 --> 00:06:40.439
Shengzi!

00:06:48.000 --> 00:06:48.800
Shengzi!

00:06:54.720 --> 00:06:55.519
Shengzi!

00:06:57.160 --> 00:06:58.000
Shengzi!

00:07:01.079 --> 00:07:01.839
What's all the noise?

00:07:01.839 --> 00:07:03.319
Weren't you told to wait over there?

00:07:03.319 --> 00:07:04.279
My brother is gone!

00:07:04.279 --> 00:07:05.439
Where am I supposed to wait?

00:07:05.519 --> 00:07:06.560
What do you mean, gone?

00:07:06.560 --> 00:07:08.079
Zhao Fengsheng has already been wheeled out of the OR.

00:07:08.079 --> 00:07:09.040
What are you doing?

00:07:10.560 --> 00:07:11.360
Wheeled out?

00:07:13.680 --> 00:07:14.879
Wasn't he inside?

00:07:14.959 --> 00:07:16.199
Zhao Fengsheng was in OR two.

00:07:16.199 --> 00:07:17.399
The one inside is OR three.

00:07:19.680 --> 00:07:20.240
Crying...

00:07:21.160 --> 00:07:22.279
...at the wrong grave.

00:07:24.120 --> 00:07:26.319
Also, Zhao Fengsheng asked me to give you a message.

00:07:26.680 --> 00:07:27.480
Go on.

00:07:27.639 --> 00:07:28.759
One of you has a voice like a duck,

00:07:28.759 --> 00:07:29.759
the other is like Sun Erniang.

00:07:29.759 --> 00:07:30.759
Learn from the quiet one.

00:07:30.759 --> 00:07:31.800
Stop howling.

00:07:34.720 --> 00:07:35.519
This...

00:07:35.639 --> 00:07:37.000
sounds like something Shengzi would say.

00:07:37.199 --> 00:07:38.639
Shengzi is okay.

00:07:38.639 --> 00:07:39.560
He's okay.

00:07:40.680 --> 00:07:41.600
He's okay.

00:07:42.040 --> 00:07:43.120
It's good that he's okay.

00:07:43.279 --> 00:07:44.279
It's good that he's okay.

00:07:44.839 --> 00:07:46.360
I'm going to find that jerk Zhao Fengsheng

00:07:46.360 --> 00:07:47.240
and settle the score.

00:07:47.720 --> 00:07:48.920
You jerk!

00:07:49.759 --> 00:07:50.839
I'm going to kill you!

00:07:50.839 --> 00:07:51.800
Wait for me!

00:07:59.959 --> 00:08:01.040
All these years

00:08:01.800 --> 00:08:03.319
I've finally obtained it.

00:08:04.560 --> 00:08:08.920
From a mere street vendor to the King of Bian Shui.

00:08:10.920 --> 00:08:11.720
From now on,

00:08:11.879 --> 00:08:15.720
my Tang family will be Bian Shui's number one clan.

00:08:17.480 --> 00:08:18.800
With this gold,

00:08:18.879 --> 00:08:20.079
what is the Li family?

00:08:20.160 --> 00:08:21.279
What is Li Xiangping?

00:08:22.839 --> 00:08:23.639
Second Master.

00:08:24.079 --> 00:08:24.720
The people from the Old Street

00:08:24.720 --> 00:08:26.319
are already trapped in the casino by us.

00:08:27.120 --> 00:08:29.040
Before I finish mining this gold,

00:08:29.160 --> 00:08:30.639
keep them cooped up in the casino.

00:08:30.759 --> 00:08:31.879
Anyone who dares to come out,

00:08:32.159 --> 00:08:33.279
just kill them.

00:08:33.440 --> 00:08:34.039
Good.

00:08:41.840 --> 00:08:42.639
Second Master.

00:08:43.039 --> 00:08:43.960
The Qian father and daughter

00:08:43.960 --> 00:08:45.639
have been captured and brought to the mine entrance.

00:08:46.240 --> 00:08:47.039
Excellent.

00:08:47.840 --> 00:08:49.399
Today is the day my Tang family

00:08:49.840 --> 00:08:51.600
dominates Bian Shui.

00:08:55.519 --> 00:08:56.360
Foolish son.

00:08:57.080 --> 00:08:59.200
All of this is yours.

00:09:00.840 --> 00:09:01.559
Let's go.

00:09:10.440 --> 00:09:11.120
Let go!

00:09:11.759 --> 00:09:12.559
Let go!

00:09:14.360 --> 00:09:14.879
Let go!

00:09:15.080 --> 00:09:15.679
Let go!

00:09:15.879 --> 00:09:16.679
Let go!

00:09:19.519 --> 00:09:20.440
Tang Hongtu!

00:09:22.399 --> 00:09:23.600
Kidnapping people at gunpoint...

00:09:24.240 --> 00:09:25.279
Aren't you afraid of the Li family's

00:09:25.600 --> 00:09:27.399
retaliation, Second Master?

00:09:29.039 --> 00:09:29.559
Dad.

00:09:29.559 --> 00:09:29.840
You...

00:09:29.840 --> 00:09:30.639
Retaliation?

00:09:31.360 --> 00:09:33.240
From now on, when Li Xiangping sees me,

00:09:33.240 --> 00:09:35.159
he'll have to call me Young Master Tang.

00:09:36.440 --> 00:09:38.639
You, Second Master Tang, boast of being self-made,

00:09:39.000 --> 00:09:40.559
but you're clearly just a bunch of robbers!

00:09:41.600 --> 00:09:42.960
In a place like Bian Shui,

00:09:43.159 --> 00:09:45.519
having the toughest fist is what rules.

00:09:50.960 --> 00:09:51.759
Get out of the way!

00:09:51.960 --> 00:09:52.759
You jerk!

00:09:52.759 --> 00:09:53.879
Still defying me?

00:09:54.320 --> 00:09:55.480
Don't move if you want to live!

00:09:55.480 --> 00:09:56.120
Otherwise, I'll...

00:09:56.120 --> 00:09:57.840
make you end up like Zhao Fengsheng.

00:09:58.360 --> 00:09:59.279
Zhao Fengsheng?

00:09:59.639 --> 00:10:00.519
What happened to him?

00:10:01.000 --> 00:10:03.120
Don't tell me you like Zhao Fengsheng too?

00:10:03.519 --> 00:10:04.480
What a pity.

00:10:05.279 --> 00:10:08.080
My old man shot him dead.

00:10:11.519 --> 00:10:12.519
He's dead?

00:10:13.200 --> 00:10:14.519
How could he die?

00:10:15.679 --> 00:10:16.559
Qian Tianyu.

00:10:17.399 --> 00:10:19.639
There's a huge gold mine down there.

00:10:19.799 --> 00:10:21.960
How wonderful it would be

00:10:22.039 --> 00:10:23.600
for us to have our fun down there.

00:10:23.799 --> 00:10:24.399
Let go!

00:10:24.399 --> 00:10:25.159
Jerk!

00:10:25.279 --> 00:10:26.000
Let her go, you...

00:10:26.000 --> 00:10:26.759
Let go!

00:10:26.759 --> 00:10:27.639
What are you doing?!

00:10:27.679 --> 00:10:28.759
Don't move if you want to live!

00:10:28.759 --> 00:10:29.279
Dad!

00:10:29.279 --> 00:10:30.600
I won't let you touch Tianyu!

00:10:30.799 --> 00:10:31.600
Second Master Tang!

00:10:32.159 --> 00:10:34.000
Aren't you the one who values your reputation most?

00:10:34.399 --> 00:10:36.120
How can you just watch your precious son

00:10:36.120 --> 00:10:38.559
do such a beastly thing?

00:10:39.320 --> 00:10:40.159
Reputation...

00:10:40.519 --> 00:10:41.879
is hard-earned.

00:10:42.960 --> 00:10:43.759
Therefore,

00:10:44.600 --> 00:10:46.840
if people are dead, they can't talk, can they?

00:10:48.840 --> 00:10:49.679
What do you mean?

00:10:49.960 --> 00:10:50.840
What do I mean?

00:10:51.759 --> 00:10:53.519
Do you know why we brought you here?

00:10:54.360 --> 00:10:57.039
In a moment, we'll kill you,

00:10:57.799 --> 00:10:59.720
and toss you right into this mine lake.

00:11:00.480 --> 00:11:03.200
The Qian family will vanish

00:11:05.120 --> 00:11:06.039
from Bian Shui forever.

00:11:08.200 --> 00:11:09.000
You...

00:11:10.120 --> 00:11:11.600
You're not even human!

00:11:12.759 --> 00:11:13.960
My precious Tianyu.

00:11:14.200 --> 00:11:16.519
If you serve me well in a moment,

00:11:16.799 --> 00:11:18.360
I might not have the heart to kill you.

00:11:19.519 --> 00:11:21.919
You could live on as my slave.

00:11:22.759 --> 00:11:23.200
Come on.

00:11:23.200 --> 00:11:23.759
Let go!

00:11:23.759 --> 00:11:24.399
Let's go!

00:11:24.519 --> 00:11:25.639
You jerk!

00:11:25.840 --> 00:11:26.279
Let go!

00:11:26.279 --> 00:11:27.279
I'll fight you to the death!

00:11:31.320 --> 00:11:31.960
Dad!

00:11:32.000 --> 00:11:32.679
You old fool!

00:11:32.679 --> 00:11:33.360
Dad!

00:11:33.360 --> 00:11:33.799
Dad!

00:11:33.919 --> 00:11:34.399
Dad!

00:11:34.840 --> 00:11:36.039
I'll deal with you!

00:11:36.559 --> 00:11:37.679
Tianyu, my dear.

00:11:37.879 --> 00:11:38.639
Kneel down.

00:11:39.279 --> 00:11:40.519
Call me Master.

00:11:41.000 --> 00:11:43.279
Or I'll blow your father's brains out.

00:11:44.840 --> 00:11:45.519
Dad...

00:11:45.840 --> 00:11:46.679
Say it!

00:12:06.960 --> 00:12:07.840
Tang Huiyao!

00:12:09.279 --> 00:12:11.120
Your grandpa Zhao Fengsheng is here!